 Andrew Olaniyi, Philip Pius, and Victor Busayo talk about how the Alpha course changed their lives on this week’s episode of “Colours of Life“. The Alpha course is an evangelistic course that seeks to introduce the basics of the Christian faith through a series of talks and discussions. Its organisers describe it as “an opportunity to explore the meaning of life.” Watch the video below:   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 